cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image processing and denoising, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The use of a structure tensor to locally control the domain kernel suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) category. The optimization of parameters using Stein's unbiased risk estimate (SURE) indicates that the paper may also be relevant to the information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories.
